{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"17a48107-828e-4321-b4eb-feb2c205c173","content":"You're on **MSTest 3.8.2** with .NET 9. Here's the recommended pattern:\n\n**`TestContext`** — declare a public property; MSTest injects it automatically:\n\n```csharp\npublic TestContext TestContext { get; set; }\n```\n\n**Sync + async init** — `[TestInitialize]` supports `async Task`, so put everything in one method:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests\n{\n    public TestContext TestContext { get; set; }\n\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task Setup()\n    {\n        // Sync work\n        // ...\n\n        // Async work\n        await SomeServiceAsync();\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task MyTest()\n    {\n        TestContext.WriteLine(\"Running test\");\n        // ...\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- `[TestInitialize]` can return `void` (sync) or `Task` (async) — no need for separate methods.\n- `[ClassInitialize]` / `[ClassCleanup]` also support `async Task` for one-time setup.\n- The constructor works for simple sync-only init, but `[TestInitialize]` is preferred since it has access to `TestContext`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"007e80ae-eaa2-4aba-a860-a076e7d89e67","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"They're using MSTest 3.8.2 on .NET 9.0. In modern MSTest (v3+), the recommended approach is:\n\n1. **TestContext injection**: Use a property `public TestContext TestContext { get; set; }` — MSTest automatically sets it.\n2. **Sync initialization**: Use `[TestInitialize]` method.\n3. **Async initialization**: `[TestInitialize]` can be `async Task` in MSTest v3.\n\nLet me give them a concise, accurate answer.\n\nActually, in MSTest v3.6+, there's also the newer constructor-based DI approach. But the classic approach is still the standard.\n\n\nFor MSTest 3.8.2, the cleanest pattern is injecting `TestContext` via a property and using `async Task` in `[TestInitialize]` for any async setup work — both `[ClassInitialize]` and `[ClassCleanup]` also support async in this version.","outputTokens":657,"requestId":"5C2D:1909B6:1F85D6D:23FBC56:69F55302"},"id":"37fb0da8-5029-4beb-8e32-8d7b93127785","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:27:45.000Z","parentId":"bf68a0ea-d490-484c-942e-ecd182664fe1"}
